cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with shape recognition and comparison using 3D models, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The method also relies on a data-driven approach, which involves learning from a shape repository, making it relevant to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper uses multi-view depth images, which are commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) research.
